---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Cookie Policy | Tom Pickup"
  description="Cookie policy for tompickup.co.uk. Information about what cookies this website uses."
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: 18 March 2026</p>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <h2>What Are Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files stored on your device by websites you visit. They are
          widely used to make websites work, remember your preferences, and provide information
          to site owners.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies This Website Uses</h2>
        <p>
          This website is a static site hosted on GitHub Pages. It uses very few cookies:
        </p>

        <div class="cookie-table-wrap">
          <table class="cookie-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Cookie</th>
                <th>Purpose</th>
                <th>Type</th>
                <th>Duration</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><code>cookie_notice</code></td>
                <td>Remembers that you have seen the cookie notice</td>
                <td>Strictly necessary</td>
                <td>1 year</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2>Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Google Fonts:</strong> This website loads fonts from Google's servers
          (<code>fonts.googleapis.com</code> and <code>fonts.gstatic.com</code>). Google
          may set cookies or use other tracking technologies when serving font files. See
          Google's
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/cookies" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">cookie policy</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>GitHub Pages:</strong> The hosting provider (GitHub/Microsoft) may set
          cookies for operational purposes. See GitHub's
          <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-cookies" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">cookie information</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>What This Website Does Not Use</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>No analytics cookies (no Google Analytics, no Cloudflare Analytics)</li>
          <li>No advertising or marketing cookies</li>
          <li>No social media tracking cookies or pixels</li>
          <li>No session or authentication cookies</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          You can control and delete cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers
          allow you to refuse cookies or delete existing ones. Note that blocking all cookies
          may affect the functionality of some websites.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Chrome</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/clear-cookies-and-site-data-firefox" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Firefox</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/en-gb/guide/safari/sfri11471/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Safari</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/delete-cookies-in-microsoft-edge-63947406-40ac-c3b8-57b9-2a946a29ae09" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Microsoft Edge</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Under the Privacy and Electronic Communications Regulations (PECR) and UK GDPR,
          you have the right to control what cookies are placed on your device. For more
          information about your data rights, see the <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          This policy may be updated if the website begins using additional cookies or
          third-party services. The date at the top of this page shows when it was last
          revised.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 7rem 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .legal-updated {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--separator);
  }

  .legal-content h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .legal-content p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .legal-content ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .legal-content ul li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .legal-content ul li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 10px;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .legal-content a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .legal-content strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .legal-content code {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* Cookie table */
  .cookie-table-wrap {
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .cookie-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .cookie-table th,
  .cookie-table td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--separator);
  }

  .cookie-table th {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .cookie-table td {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .cookie-table td code {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page {
      padding: 6rem 0 var(--space-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
